expand_less 

<appender name="LOGSTASH" class="net.logstash.logback.appender.LogstashTcpSocketAppender"> 
   <destination>logstash-load-balancer:5044</destination> 
   <encoder class="net.logstash.logback.encoder.LogstashEncoder" /> 
    
   <!-- Safety: If Logstash is down, keep 10,000 records in memory to retry --> 
   <queueSize>10000</queueSize> 
</appender> 

2. Logstash Configuration (middleman.conf) 

We tell Logstash to listen and then ship to Elasticsearch. 

code Bash 

